item.description: SoftLayer_Account_Partner_Business Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Account_Partner_Business data type contains specific information concerning an Account’s relationship with Business Partner Data, in the form of the Account’s Country Experience Identifier (CEID), Channel ID, and Segment ID. Local channelId The Channel ID associated with the Account. Type: integer countryEnterpriseCode The Country Enterprise Code associated with the Account. Type: string segmentId The Segment ID associated with the Account.
